                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7829" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1216</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1977 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">不期而遇,相伴相惜:海南航空的“东方待客之道”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Meeting by Chance and Accompanying by Mutual Cherish: the &quot;Oriental Hospitality&quot; of Hainan Airlines</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">余洁，吴泉蓉，张乐新，韩艺，刘亚杰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">余洁，吴泉蓉，张乐新，韩艺，刘亚杰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海南航空</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海南航空；东方文化；航空服务；差异化营销；服务创新；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hainan Airlines; oriental culture; airline services; differentiated marketing; service innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着中国旅游业快速发展，民航业也迎来了巨大机遇，提升服务品质成为航空公司竞争的焦点。本案例以海南航空破产重组为背景，讲述了海南航空如何在竞争激烈的市场中坚守东方待客之道，发展一系列高质量航空服务产品。主要运用差异化营销理论，同时借助STP理论、SWOT分析，从有形展示、产品、服务、价格和促销活动方面解析了海南航空的差异化服务营销策略。案例介绍了海南航空独特的飞机彩绘和“梦之羽”视觉识别系统，以及富有地域文化特色的机上餐食。还涵盖了海航金鹏俱乐部的常客计划，以及“梦享、海享、关怀”系列服务项目。此外，案例还提及了海南航空具有价格优势的机票促销活动。这一系列策略突显了海南航空服务中融入了中国文化、地方文化和企业文化特色，以不断创新差异化的航空服务。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the rapid growth of China&#39;s tourism industry, the civil aviation sector has also witnessed tremendous opportunities, with an increased focus on elevating service quality becoming the focal point of competition among airlines. This case study, set against the backdrop of Hainan Airlines&#39; bankruptcy and restructuring, narrates how Hainan Airlines adhered to the principles of Eastern hospitality and developed a series of high-quality aviation service products in a fiercely competitive market. Primarily utilizing the differentiation marketing theory and leveraging STP theory and SWOT analysis, this case study dissects Hainan Airlines&#39; strategies for differentiated service marketing across various dimensions: tangible presentation, products, services, pricing, and promotional activities. The case study introduces Hainan Airlines&#39; unique aircraft livery and the &quot;Dream Feather&quot; visual identity system, along with in-flight meals infused with regional cultural characteristics. It also covers the Hainan Golden Phoenix Club, the frequent flyer program, and the &quot;Dream, Explore, Care&quot; series of service initiatives. Additionally, the case study mentions Hainan Airlines&#39; promotional activities leveraging price advantages. This series of strategies underscores how Hainan Airlines has incorporated elements of Chinese culture, regional culture, and corporate culture into its services, continually innovating differentiated aviation services.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《服务营销》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">差异化服务营销，解构为有形展示差异化，产品差异化，服务差异化，价格差异化，促销活动差异化;STP理论；SWOT环境分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
